Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:25.33,Static Texts,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs193\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1\b1\\pos(328.14,667.857)}Versus
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:25.33,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs163\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\\b1\pos(325.144,784.858)}Ambassador Hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:28.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:32.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With its armies \Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:36.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadow\N threatens us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:40.14,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,But I'll fight to maintain\N the peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:43.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:47.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:50.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:53.86,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:58.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:02.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:04.67,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:08.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:13.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:16.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:40.12,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs68\bord5.1\fnCalibri\4aFF\1c&H4B4D4B&\3c&HE6F3F2&\b1\an8\pos(867.2,217.4)}East Japan Road Race Championship\N{\fs39.1}Organizer: J{\1c&H6461B3&}A{\1c&H4B4D4B&}O     With Support From: {\1c&H6461B3&}Suzuki Motors
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:38.57,Default Top,,0,0,0,, - Go for it!\N- You can do it! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs68\bord5.1\fnCalibri\4aFF\1c&HECF5ED&\3c&H525C31&\fad(300,300)\b1\an4\pos(215,424)}Start
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:46.71,Default Top,,0,0,0,,- Do your best!\N- You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do your best!\N- Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta get first place!{絶対 １位になるのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:19.24,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,Taki! Hongo! {You must win it!}{滝 本郷 がっちりいただけよ}Don't lose, ya hear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.08,0:02:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo and Taki are nearing the target location.{本郷と滝が 目標地点に近づいています}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Failure will not be tolerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim carefully{狙いを正確に}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and get rid of Hongo and Taki in one foul swoop!{本郷と滝を 一撃で始末するのだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How strange. It seems that we've gone off course.{おかしい\Nコースを間違えたらしい}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's with that helicopter?}{何だ あのヘリは？}Is that a helicopter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have an announcement regarding the race.{レースの状況を お知らせします\Nレースの状況を お知らせします\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:45.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat, we have an announcement regarding the race.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:53.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The two racers in the lead, from Tachibana Racing Club,{トップをきっていた\N立花レーシングクラブの２台が\i0} {\i1}\Nappear to have gone off course, and are missing.{コースを間違えたのか\N行方不明になっています\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:06:00.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taki Kazuya and Hongo Takeshi of Tachibana\N Racing Club were in the lead, however...{\i0}{先頭}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!{行ってみよう}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not here!{いないぞ\N確かに命中したはずだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure we hit them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.69,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{Looking for something?}{捜し物かね？}Looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.13,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{Stop a moment!}{ちょっと待って}Hold on a minute, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's tire tracks heading that way!{そっちにも タイヤの跡があるな}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's check it out!{itte miyou}\N- Let's go that way!{こっちへ行きましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:40.14,Italics,,0,0,0,,Did the attack go as planned?{襲撃は成功したか}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir. {We have confirmed the corpses of Hongo Takeshi and Taki Kazuya.}\NWe've confirmed the deaths of Hongo Takeshi and Taki Kazuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:49.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,Good. Return immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is Shocker's Tokyo branch?{ここがショッカーの東京支部か}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:15.01,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{We'll be able to crush their new scheme!}{やつらの新しい計画を\Nぶち壊してやれるな}Time to stop whatever their new plan is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! They're on to us!{しまった\N感づかれたか}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:09:01.27,Italics,,0,0,0,,{You two sure walked in here nonchalantly, Hongo and Taki.}{２人揃ってノコノコやってきたな\N本郷　滝} Hongo and Taki, you've done us \Na favor by coming right to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:11.44,Italics,Flame,0,0,0,,{Your movements are all being tracked by hidden Shocker cameras!}{貴様たちの行動は すべて ショッカーの隠しカメラで\Nお見通しなのだ}Shocker's hidden cameras have captured\N your every movement! {Die in there!}Now stay still and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's poison gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, we need to open that escape hatch!{滝 あの脱出口を開け}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's holding it down!{誰か上にいる}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to open it if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice, it's Kabutrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good, I can't breathe!{ダメだ 息が詰まる}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:49.61,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,With this, the two of them\N should be completely melted!{これで２人は 完全に溶けたはずだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It went well!\N They've both turned into soup!{うまくいった\Nみんな溶けてしまった}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right, Kabutrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That voice belongs to Kamen Rider!{何？その声は仮面ライダー}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten my abilities?{貴様 俺の威力を忘れたのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you live, Kamen Rider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,where are you, Ambassador Hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nut's, so he's fled?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have not fled .
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:18.45,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,Shocker has successfully built an\Nimpenetrable stronghold in a secret location.{ショッカーは すでに秘密の場所に 大要塞を完成した}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:23.83,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{If we set up the Super Destructive Light Beam in this great stronghold...}{その大要塞に スーパー破壊光線をセットすれば}And pnce we set up our Super Destruction Beam there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...we will be able to call forth lightning all \Nover Japan, and reduce it to ashes!{日本全土に 自由に雷を起こし 焼き払えるのだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In 30 seconds, the base you're\N in will be blown to smithereens!{あと30秒で そのアジトは こっぱみじんになる}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They've set a time bomb! \NTaki, let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:50.83,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{You will not break that down with that strength of yours!}{貴様の力では壊れん}Your strength alone can't break through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:55.32,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{It was made according to calculations by Shocker's computer.}{ショッカーのコンピューターが\N計算して作ったものだ}We built that door in accordance to\Ncalculations made by Shocker's computers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You have 15 seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Kamen Rider and Taki Kazuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, there's no other way to escape\N besides finding that time bomb!{時限爆弾を発見する以外に\N助かる方法はないぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He said there were only 15 seconds left?{今 15秒って言ったな？\Nシーッ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, there's no time left!{ライダー 時間がないぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:49.14,Italics,Flame,0,0,0,,{Ambassador Hell, the base was blown up successfully.}Ambassador Hell, The bases \Nself-destruction was successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:51.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider's been wiped \Noff the face of the Earth!{仮面ライダーは地上から抹殺です}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:54.04,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{There might be that unlikely possibility.}{万が一ということもある}There's a minuscule chance that they survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.04,Italics,Flame,0,0,0,,{It can't be...}Surely you jest...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We must take the necessary measures.{打つべき手は打ってある}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:05.19,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{Until we transport the Super Destructive Light Beam Device in this truck to the great stronghold at Mount Fuji...}{あのトラックに積んだ\Nスーパー破壊光線装置を 富士山の大要塞に運ぶまでは}Until we transport the Super Destruction Beam device \Nto our impenetrable stronghold at Mount Fuji,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,do not let your guard down even for a second.{念には念を入れるのだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi and Taki sure are late.{遅いなあ 猛たちは}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:22.57,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{They must be beating up Shocker!}{きっとショッカーを\Nやっつけてるわよ}They're probably busy \Nbeating up Shocker right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.57,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{I wonder if I should go make the food.}{私 ごちそうでも作っとこうかしら}Should I cook something while we wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- And a strange one at that!\N- It's an earthquake!{妙な揺れだな}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, the floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The floor's glowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:44.97,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,A new Shocker monster!{ショッカーの新怪人！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:50.85,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{It's me, Longhorn Kid!}The name's Kamikirikid!\N Now come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.52,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{And we'd just listen to you? Are you an idiot?}{来いと言われて 行くバカがあるか}What kind of idiot would come with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare to fight back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat my sleeping gas!{俺の しびれガスをくらえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and carry them out of here!{早く こいつらを運び出せ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The cups still warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops isn't the kind of person \Nwho leaves his pipe lit.{パイプの火を\Nつけっぱなしにしとくなんて おやじさんらしくもない}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hongo!\N- Tokko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and get out!{早く降りるんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.51,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,A new Shocker monster?{ショッカーの新怪人か}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The name's Kamikirikid!{俺はカミキリキッドだ\Nこれを受けてみろ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,799)}Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Shocker's great stronghold located?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts...{苦しい… 言う\N言うから この手を緩めてくれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk! I'll talk, so let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in Fuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in Fuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you attack me?{どうして俺がやられるんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{Because you're a blockhead!}{貴様がマヌケだからだ}It's what you deserve, you imbecile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How vexing...{悔しい…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider.{ライダー ショッカーのトラックが\N富士山に向かっているぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:19:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A truck with a Shocker crest is heading towards Mount Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of Emi and Tokko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They're over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tail Shocker all the way to their stronghold.{どこまでも追って\Nｼｮｯｶｰの要塞を突きとめてやる}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll realize soon enough.{今に見ていろ 仮面ライダーめ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{Stupid Kamen Rider.}How foolish you are, Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:19:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That smoke...{あの煙は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think you'd be able to escape with that?{そんなことで\N逃げられると思うのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rats! I lost them.{しまった　見失ったか}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.79,0:23:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So the entrance to Shocker's stronghold is in this field?{この草原に\Nショッカーの大要塞の入り口が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.51,0:23:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:35.72,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{Try resisting even a bit, and your allies will lose their lives!}{少しでも手向かってみろ 貴様の仲間の命はない\Nあれを見ろ}If you resist, even for a second,\N then your friends' lives are forfeit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.88,0:23:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops! Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.61,0:23:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, don't worry about us!{ライダー 俺たちに構うな}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I'm prepared for this!{うよ　諦めてるわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.15,0:23:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you willing to defy us now?{これでも俺たちに刃向かう気か}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:08.83,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Race, race, machine! Run like lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:15.88,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,And carry all our hopes with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.88,0:21:19.80,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Take out those dastardly Shockers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:26.64,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Dive, Cyclone! Straight into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:34.27,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Hurricane Jump! Hurricane Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:41.94,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you! Cyclone! Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:22:03.76,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Race, race, machine! Speed like a fireball!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:11.06,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Become the limbs of the ally of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.06,0:22:14.81,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Reclaim the cheerfulness of our towns
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:22.19,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Soar into the sky, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:29.41,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Hurricane Jump! Hurricane Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:37.21,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,It's a victory! Cyclone! Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.78,0:23:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.08,0:23:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just sit by and watch them die.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.62,0:23:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.93,0:24:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.98,0:24:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do a thing to us!{手も足も出まい}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.90,0:24:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Secure the ropes!{縄をかけろ}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.67,0:24:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.38,0:24:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are going to give up, Rider?{参ったか ライダー}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.39,0:25:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Drag him around!{引きずり回せ}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.20,0:25:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue fighting, don't give in!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.33,0:25:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.96,0:25:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, I'm coming!{ライダー　今 俺も行くぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.65,0:25:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!{滝さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.15,0:25:57.89,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{Accursed Shocker! You'll pay for this!}{チキショー ショッカーの野郎\Nただじゃおかねえぞ}Damn you, Shocker! \NYou'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.67,0:26:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.75,0:26:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, I'll take care of the Pops and Yuri!{ライダー\Nおやじさんとユリは引き受けた}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.55,0:26:19.88,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.22,0:26:23.24,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.72,0:26:27.38,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.38,0:26:30.66,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.90,0:26:34.39,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.39,0:26:37.80,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.13,0:26:41.23,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.78,0:26:44.58,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.37,0:26:48.89,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.89,0:26:52.14,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.39,0:26:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.59,0:26:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat! Retreat!{引け　引け！}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.27,0:27:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rider's gone.{ライダーがいない\Nそんな… たった今まで}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.36,0:27:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! He was there\N just a second ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.98,0:27:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.24,0:27:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.45,0:27:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tear down Shocker's stronghold \Non my own if I have to!{俺１人でもショッカーの\N大要塞をたたき壊してやる}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.01,0:27:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.26,0:27:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So Shocker constructed their great \Nstronghold inside of Mount Fuji?{あの富士山の中に ｼｮｯｶｰ大要塞を造り上げたのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.43,0:27:44.68,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{If that's the case, I'll brute force my way through their cordon!}{こうなりゃ力ずくでも 警戒線を突破してやる}In that case, I'll have to force my way through enemy lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.68,0:27:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hongo!\N Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.35,0:27:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't rush, Taki.{慌てるな 滝\N見ろ 目的はあれだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.14,0:27:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.35,0:27:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.28,0:28:01.63,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{That's what we have to destroy, to take Shocker by surprise.}{ショッカーの不意をついて あれを破壊することが大切だ}We have to use the element of \Nsurprise and destroy that first.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.62,0:28:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.96,0:28:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.51,0:28:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.38,0:29:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters!{怪人ども}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.64,0:29:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea Snake Man!{海蛇男}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.06,0:29:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Worm Man!{ミミズ男}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.27,0:29:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Eiking!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.64,0:29:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghoster!{ゴースター\Nユニコルノス}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.06,0:29:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pranodon!{プラノドン}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.90,0:29:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinokomorg!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.03,0:29:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Zanjioh!{ザンジオー}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.32,0:29:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dokumond!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.12,0:29:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Musasabeedle!{ムササビドール\Nサラセニアン}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.24,0:29:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Zanbronzo!{ザンブロンゾ}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.00,0:29:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Beaded Lizard Man!{毒トカゲ男}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.16,0:29:35.75,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{Hongo Takeshi, good job coming all the way here!}{本郷猛 はるばるご苦労}Hongo Takeshi, you've done well coming here!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.75,0:29:38.88,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{Your efforts are commendable, but this will be where your grave lies!}{せっかくだが ここが貴様の墓場だ}But alas, this place will be your grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.88,0:29:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.34,0:29:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, Taki?{滝 いいか\N任せとけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.44,0:29:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.31,0:30:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, You go and blow up the stronghold!{滝 行け　要塞を爆破しろ}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.52,0:30:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.11,0:30:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,799)}Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.51,0:31:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.63,0:31:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.84,0:31:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,While you were busy fighting us, {...we fully installed the Destructive Light Beam Device at the great stronghold!}{大要塞の破壊光線装置は\N完全に備えつけられたのだ}we finished installing \Nthe Destruction Beam device on our stronghold!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.18,0:31:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be fired at Tokyo in a matter of seconds!{今頃は東京に向けて\N発射の秒読みの頃だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.72,0:31:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What? In a few seconds?{何 秒読み？}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.35,0:32:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, this time Shocker has won!{ライダー\N俺たち ショッカーの勝ちだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.50,0:32:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Target of attack, Tokyo Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.67,0:32:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser firing in 30 seconds.{レーザー発射 30秒前}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.55,0:32:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fine mess I've stumbled into..{まずいことになりやがった}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.85,0:32:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.61,0:32:41.85,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{That Tokyo Tower will soon become like heavens.}{今に あの東京タワーを\Nアメのようにしてやる}Soon, the Tokyo Tower will be blown to smithereens.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.89,0:32:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.89,0:32:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you get in here?{いつのまに入ってきた？}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.08,0:33:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Taki!\N- Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.08,0:33:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right!\N- Those dials are the controls!{そのダイヤルだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.30,0:33:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try to fire the laser now, \Nthe entire stronghold will blow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.97,0:33:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to stop it quickly!{おい 早くやめさせろ}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.47,0:33:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late!\N{もう遅い　この要塞は爆発するぞ} This stronghold's about to blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.90,0:33:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right!\N- Taki, let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.12,0:33:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!{何事だ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.12,0:33:44.83,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{The power room has been sabotaged by Kamen Rider!}{仮面ﾗｲﾀﾞｰに動力室がやられました}Kamen Rider has destroyed the power room!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.83,0:33:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.87,0:33:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.04,0:33:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All units, evacuate!{全員 退避！}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.73,0:34:10.22,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.32,0:34:13.85,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.85,0:34:17.57,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.57,0:34:21.16,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.16,0:34:24.76,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.76,0:34:28.61,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.61,0:34:31.51,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.05,0:34:34.55,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.55,0:34:39.03,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.03,0:34:42.28,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.80,0:34:53.13,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.47,0:34:56.49,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.97,0:35:00.63,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.63,0:35:03.91,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.15,0:35:07.64,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.64,0:35:11.05,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.97,0:35:14.48,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.03,0:35:17.83,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.62,0:35:22.14,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.14,0:35:25.39,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.44,0:34:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Reversal!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.61,0:34:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.91,0:35:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that, Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.79,0:35:09.50,Default,Flame,0,0,0,,{You'll never defy Shocker again!}{二度とショッカーに 刃向かえなくしてやる}I'll make it so you can't \Ndefy Shocker ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.08,0:35:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! His power's are in his horns?{クソ あのツノか}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.63,0:35:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.02,0:35:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.87,0:35:54.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.34,0:35:57.09,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.09,0:35:59.09,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.09,0:36:02.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.72,0:36:04.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.51,0:36:06.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.52,0:36:08.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.10,0:36:09.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.10,0:36:12.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.15,0:36:17.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.65,0:36:21.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.32,0:36:24.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.45,0:36:29.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Kamen Rider!
